{"tid":877342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角單位閉門失火 消防火場救出2貓慘死","createTime":"2018-10-26T09:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T09:38:20.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0029d78eb00dafbb8ce10916cc1baa69bec51e16","tid":877342,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181026/large/1540542891_05e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F1540542891_05e7.jpg&h=f0926af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防員即場為兩貓進行急救，可惜最終經搶救後不治。(梁澤岡攝)<br />\n<br />\n旺角山東街36號華美大廈樓上一單位，下午2時33分，單位突閉門失火，冒出濃煙，消防接報到場出動一喉一煙帽隊撲救，約16分鐘將火救熄，火警原因有待調查。消防在火場先後救出兩隻貓，惟牠們已奄奄一息，消防員即場為兩貓進行急救，愛護動物協會人員亦接獲通知到場處理，惟兩貓最終經搶救後不治，由愛協人員撿走。<br />\n<br />\n曾協助救貓的導盲犬導師胡清怡表示曾對貓兒急救，惟牠並無反應，手腳沒有郁動，「大家都努力搶救梗。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181026/58838682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181026%2F58838682&d=pBvlUjHteML23fzRuHOJCo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5039b302\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181026%2F58838682&h=481dad72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181026/58838682</a>"},{"pid":"26636454a67d0fb7e56f1538b130ae2742b4caac","tid":877342,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e6d38638cd90f6c61b170283893714d5b4dddd","tid":877342,"uid":52881,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"仲以為係消防員為左救貓慘死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}